Package com.example.StudentManagement.entity

Class Exam

java.lang.Object
com.example.StudentManagement.entity.Exam
public class Exam extends Object
This class represents an Exam entity in the application. It has properties to store exam information such as assessmentID, title, location, startTime, endTime, moduleCode, grade, and studentID.
Author:
Jiaming LIU
